This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chef thai
des: Ever wanted to learn how to cook Thai food? Chef Thai can help you out! Chef Thai knows how to make the top four popular dishes in Thailand! Currently Chef Thai focuses on the dishes: chicken pad thai, pad see ew, pineapple fried rice, and tom yum! Just ask Chef Thai to get started!
